{"tid":2134171,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"前日國安法拉四個人 琴日DQ 今日延期 國際有咩反應","createTime":"2020-07-31T13:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T14:45:47.000Z","uid":13321,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"99ee81d364adccdc5693cf55f2e9707dad89cc16","tid":2134171,"uid":13321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:36:03.000Z","msg":"唔好意思跟得唔夠貼 求source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日香港發生左咁多事<br />\n前日用國安法拉左四個手足 話佢地顛倒國家安全<br />\n琴日DQ左十二個候選議員 唔夠信奉基本法<br />\n今日用緊急法延期立法會一年 <br />\n林鄭仲要話除非國際用核子手段 兩敗俱傷 <br />\n如果唔係所謂制裁對佢都唔會有咩影響<br />\n<br />\n因為宜家唯一寄望好似係國際真係可以強硬制裁<br />\n我真係好驚發生咁多事國際無理我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似除咗琴日有個英國官員譴責DQ同今日BBC出左報導立法會延期之外<br />\n我搵左好耐都好似冇乜見到國際有咩回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望國際真係可以搞撚掂中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625baf1ed474df0db494e2466fefbb7a335febc4","tid":2134171,"uid":13321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53424fdea29f66c557eba548446f5b15770767c1","tid":2134171,"uid":56819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:45:01.000Z","msg":"繼續譴責...完"},{"pid":"68dbfe968bf4ae4578a7deede966939b8ed62e24","tid":2134171,"uid":8605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"星期六日外國人唔開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bcfc33b4530a6c0af7841ee827d1254a26980b","tid":2134171,"uid":13321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" cla